- âœ… Unblock a port or port range  
- ğŸ“œ List or clear all tool-created rules  
- ğŸ”’ BLOCK ALL connections (inbound + outbound)  
- ğŸŒ ALLOW ALL connections (restore internet access)  
- ğŸ’¾ Export and Import firewall configurations  
- ğŸ“ Enable firewall logging (track dropped connections)  
- ğŸ“Š Show recent dropped connections from log  
- ğŸŒ Show IP information for awareness  
- ğŸ†“ 3 free actions without signing in  
- âœ‰ï¸ Unlimited actions after email verification  

